55:28.356 --> 55:30.323
Why are you so interested now?

55:30.389 --> 55:33.220
Oh. Oh, I don't know.

55:33.289 --> 55:37.052
Well, maybe you and I
got off to a bad start.

55:37.122 --> 55:41.146
