but I was too fast for him.

57:07.322 --> 57:11.346
He was a baby.
He didn't know how
to do those things yet.

57:11.422 --> 57:14.617
He was terrible.
He came on me
after two seconds.

57:16.488 --> 57:18.921
So I dumped him.

57:21.622 --> 57:23.851
He wrote to me for a year,

57:25.022 --> 57:27.148
but I never wrote back.

57:29.655 --> 57:33.713
<i>I remember once in the fort
we built in the forest,</i>

57:33.789 --> 57:36.154
