57:42.822 --> 57:45.687
<i>It was the first time anyone--</i>

57:45.755 --> 57:50.155
<i>[Inhales Sharply]
I'm sorry. I'm boring you
with my stories.</i>

57:50.223 --> 57:53.815
No. No, go on.
I'm enjoying it.

57:55.156 --> 57:58.350
