Go on? With what?</i>

57:58.422 --> 58:00.412
What happened to your eye?

58:02.355 --> 58:05.379
It's nothing.
Some asshole tried to hit me,

58:05.455 --> 58:07.422
but I fought back.

58:07.488 --> 58:10.580
He was bleeding like a pig.

58:10.655 --> 58:15.214
Nobody better mess with me,
because if they do,
I'll mess with them back.

58:34.755 --> 58:37.586
I suppose you don't want any?

58:37.655 --> 58:39.622
Why not?

58:39.689 --> 58:42.850
Never judge a book
by its cover.

58:42.922 --> 58:45.821
I've done my share
of smoking.

58:47.189 --> 58:49.781
- And fucking?
- Yes.

58:51.189 --> 58:54.088
